    • ShowStatus

      public MovieStatus ShowStatus()
      Get the movie status with this movie's start and end date Movie status is determine by today date, movie's start date and end date If today's date is after movie's end date, return END_OF_SHOW, Else if today's date is <7 days before start date, return PREVIEW Else if today's date is between start date and end date, return NOW_SHOWING Else, return COMING_SOON
      Returns:
      MovieStatus Movie's status based on this movie's start and end date
